headline: Keysight Introduces Two Frequency Extenders and Calibration Kit to Extend Broadband Vector Network Analyzer up to 250 GHz
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., September 09, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) introduces two new millimeter-wave frequency extender modules, the NA5305A Frequency Extender up to 170 GHz and NA5307A Frequency Extender up to 250 GHz, and the 85065A Precision Calibration Kit 0.5 mm. When used with Keysight’s PNA/PNA-X Vector Network Analyzers (VNA) and the N5292A Test Set Controller, the new accessories enable engineers to achieve fully calibrated single-sweep broadband S-parameter measurements
